This is a TODO List with (hopefully) future Cournal Features!
(The order represents some plan of next work)

* Save settings, last modified page, last work directory
* Insert / Delete Pages
* Ask before close unsaved document
* Place some colors for quick switching in the main panel
* Commandlineinterface (CLI)
* Keymapping (Ctrl+s for saving, Ctrl+o for opening a file, etc)

* Better eraser
* Selection-Tool
* Presentation modus
* A Tool to highlight text in the PDF
* Use digitizer sensitivity for pen thickness

* Support to open more than one PDF Document
* Save PDF in XOJ file

* Chat with both keyboard and handwriting compatibility
* Android Port
* Userlist
* Remember the last Server connected to
* Authentication (Username+Password or "Tablet-optimized" Password)
* Show position of other users in scrollbar
* Freehand-Tool for scrolling
